The paper discusses the design and deployment of blockchain-based applications, which involves distributed computing (cs.DC), security and privacy (cs.CR), software engineering (cs.SE), database systems (cs.DB), and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.DC and cs.CR, followed by cs.SE, cs.DB, and cs.NI.
